# Privacy Policy for SVCE Locator

**Last updated:** October 25, 2025

SVCE Locator is developed by Rajat Dashore. This app is provided free of charge and is intended for use as is.

## Information Collection and Use
SVCE Locator may collect certain information such as:
- Your email address (for login and authentication)
- Location data (for showing nearby facilities)
- Usage data (for app improvement)

All data collected is stored securely using Firebase and is **not shared** with any third parties.

## Third-party Services
The app uses the following third-party services:
- [Firebase Authentication](https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy)
- [Firebase Firestore Database](https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy)
- [Google Maps Platform](https://policies.google.com/privacy)

## Security
We value your trust and strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

## Changes to This Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. You are advised to check this page periodically for any changes.

## Contact
If you have any questions or suggestions, contact us at:
**rajatdashore@gmail.com**
